                            <h2>All students should fill in the census</h2>

                            <p>Wherever you are, from halls to your old bedroom at home, every student is legally required to complete Census 2021. You will be able to request a code to complete yours online.</p>

                            <p>You must complete the census for your university address.</p>

                            <p>If you have a separate home address in England or Wales, your family needs to include you on their household questionnaire too.</p>

                            <p>They will not need to answer all the individual questions about you. You should complete these questions on the form about your university address.</p>

                            <h3>Not at your university address?</h3>

                            <p>If you are not currently staying at your university address, you can <a href="#">request a new access code</a> to complete the census.</p>


